[24/02/2018 22:32:14] <font color="#00ff00">El baile se llama tango</font>
[24/02/2018 22:32:14] <font color="#00ff00">y es de Sudamérica.</font>
[24/02/2018 22:32:16] <font color="#00ff00">Se baila pegados.</font>
